= Game Formulas =

This page documents all mathematical formulas used in Final Fantasy Mystic Quest (SNES), including damage calculations, stat effects, and game mechanics.

== Physical Combat ==

=== Basic Attack Damage ===

<nowiki>
Step 1: Calculate Base Attack
  Base_ATK = Weapon_Attack + (Strength × 2)

Step 2: Calculate Defense
  Base_DEF = Armor_DEF + (Agility / 2)

Step 3: Raw Damage
  Raw = Base_ATK - (Base_DEF / 2)
  If Raw < 1, Raw = 1

Step 4: Apply Variance (±12.5%)
  Variance = random(-Raw/8, Raw/8)
  Damage = Raw + Variance

Step 5: Apply Weakness/Resistance
  If target is weak: Damage × 2
  If target resists: Damage × 0.5
  If target absorbs: Damage becomes healing
</nowiki>

=== Critical Hits ===

<nowiki>
Critical Rate = Speed / 256

With Charm of Valor: Critical Rate × 2

Critical Damage = Base_Damage × 2
</nowiki>

