== Experience & Levels ==

=== EXP Gain ===

<nowiki>
Battle_EXP = Sum of defeated enemy EXP
Benjamin_EXP = Battle_EXP
Partner_EXP = 0 (partners don't level)
</nowiki>

=== Level Curve ===

<nowiki>
EXP for level N = (N^3 × 15) / 2

Level 10:  7,500 total
Level 20: 60,000 total
Level 30: 202,500 total
Level 41: 517,433 total (max)
</nowiki>

