== Battlefield System ==

=== Battle Count ===

Each battlefield has 10 battles. After completion:
- Battlefield treasure appears
- Random encounters in area reduced by 50%

=== Enemy Scaling ===

<nowiki>
Battlefield enemies do NOT scale with level.
Fixed difficulty per battlefield.
</nowiki>

== Gold Mechanics ==

=== Monster Gold Drops ===

<nowiki>
Gold = Base_Gold × random(0.8, 1.2)
Rounded to nearest 10
</nowiki>

=== Shop Prices ===

<nowiki>
Buy_Price = Item_Base_Price
Sell_Price = Item_Base_Price / 2

All items can be sold at any shop.
</nowiki>

