=== Petrify Mechanic ===

<nowiki>
Axe attacks vs stone enemies:
  If enemy is "Stoneable":
    Instant kill if damage > 0

Petrifiable enemies: Golems, Statues
</nowiki>

== Escape Mechanics ==

<nowiki>
Escape is always 100% successful in FFMQ.
No formula - instant escape when selected.
Exception: Boss battles (cannot escape)
</nowiki>

== Boss Mechanics ==

=== Boss HP Thresholds ===

Bosses change behavior at HP thresholds:

<nowiki>
Phase 1: 100-66% HP (Normal attacks)
Phase 2: 66-33% HP (Stronger attacks)
Phase 3: 33-0% HP (Desperation moves)
</nowiki>

=== Final Boss (Dark King) ===

<nowiki>
Form 1 (Spider): 2000 HP, weak to Thunder
Form 2 (Dragon): 2500 HP, weak to Ice
Form 3 (Head): 3000 HP, no weakness
Form 4 (Final): 4000 HP, weak to Flare
</nowiki>

